WRITE TO @silenzio NOT ME

This is the result of three days of work, including ideas, sketches on paper and digital testing.
The intent was to create a **simple** symbol, but one with a recognizable meaning related to the idea of **community**.

The ‚ÄúC,‚Äù the initial of Community, is intertwined with the shape of a **dolphin**, chosen for its natural connection to the concept of group, communication and play - qualities that make a community come alive.
The **crown**, small and discreet, is a symbolic detail that is not meant to dominate the rest of the logo. It does not represent power, but symbolizes belonging and mutual respect within the group.
It is a simple way to enhance collective identity without putting a single individual at the center.

The **goal** was to find a balance between form and meaning, avoiding superfluous elements but creating something that would leave a mark, while maintaining a simple and intuitive style.

I don't know if I hit the target, but of one thing I am certain: I gave it my best.
**Thanks** for this opportunity. I hope you can **enjoy** what I have created.
